{"parentUuid":"97d37bea-98a2-4af0-817b-ac791d16402c","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/baotoq/Work/micro-commerce","sessionId":"3ff5df90-448e-4ed5-b95f-d6d4b72de583","version":"2.1.63","gitBranch":"master","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01A1biLeGS4n4y1Qapcv452w","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking a general knowledge question about \"agentic AI.\" This isn't related to the codebase, so I'll answer from my knowledge.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":29659,"cache_read_input_tokens":11680,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":29659},"output_tokens":10,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"}},"requestId":"req_011CYePGZtsPLSBiojbP7Ba6","type":"assistant","uuid":"cee59b80-1752-4721-a649-bbbc9b60fc61","timestamp":"2026-03-02T14:08:15.877Z"}
{"parentUuid":"cee59b80-1752-4721-a649-bbbc9b60fc61","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/baotoq/Work/micro-commerce","sessionId":"3ff5df90-448e-4ed5-b95f-d6d4b72de583","version":"2.1.63","gitBranch":"master","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01A1biLeGS4n4y1Qapcv452w","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Agentic AI refers to AI systems that can autonomously pursue goals by planning, reasoning, and taking actions over multiple steps — rather than just responding to a single prompt.\n\n**Key characteristics:**\n\n- **Goal-directed** — given a high-level objective, the agent breaks it down into sub-tasks\n- **Tool use** — interacts with external systems (APIs, databases, file systems, browsers)\n- **Multi-step reasoning** — chains together observations, decisions, and actions in a loop\n- **Memory** — maintains context across steps to inform future decisions\n- **Self-correction** — evaluates results and adjusts its approach when something fails\n\n**How it differs from standard LLM usage:**\n\n| Standard LLM | Agentic AI |\n|---|---|\n| Single prompt → single response | Goal → plan → execute → observe → repeat |\n| Stateless | Maintains working memory |\n| Human drives each step | Agent drives autonomously |\n| Text in, text out | Can call tools, write files, run code |\n\n**Common patterns:**\n\n- **ReAct** (Reason + Act) — interleave reasoning traces with tool calls\n- **Plan-and-execute** — create a plan upfront, then execute steps\n- **Reflection** — agent critiques its own output and iterates\n- **Multi-agent** — multiple specialized agents collaborate (researcher, coder, reviewer)\n\n**Real-world examples:** coding assistants (like Claude Code), research agents that search/synthesize information, customer support agents that look up accounts and take actions, DevOps agents that diagnose and fix infrastructure issues.\n\nThe core idea is shifting AI from a \"tool you query\" to an \"agent that works on your behalf.\""}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":29659,"cache_read_input_tokens":11680,"output_tokens":433,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":29659,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CYePGZtsPLSBiojbP7Ba6","type":"assistant","uuid":"bac520a7-6873-4abd-96a2-1837284446d6","timestamp":"2026-03-02T14:08:24.611Z"}
